# MyAI_Assistant_Offline
Multi-Purpose Offline AI Assistant Android App (Hindi + English) | Student, Business, Motivation &amp; Goal Helper | Fully Offline, Beginner-Friendly, Copy-Paste Ready
# My AI Assistant - Offline

*Multi-Purpose Offline Android AI App*  
•⁠  ⁠Works completely offline  
•⁠  ⁠Hindi + English support  
•⁠  ⁠Modules: Student Helper, Business Helper, Motivation, Goal Planner  
•⁠  ⁠Lightweight and beginner-friendly  
•⁠  ⁠Persistent chat across rotation  

## Features
•⁠  ⁠Friendly chat interface with RecyclerView  
•⁠  ⁠Smart Rule Engine with weighted scoring  
•⁠  ⁠Offline deterministic AI (no internet required)  
•⁠  ⁠Multi-language support (Hindi/English)  
•⁠  ⁠Copy-Paste ready project for Android Studio  
•⁠  ⁠Easily shareable APK  

## Installation
1.⁠ ⁠Clone the repository or download ZIP  
2.⁠ ⁠Open Android Studio → File → New → Import Project  
3.⁠ ⁠Let Gradle sync  
4.⁠ ⁠Connect Android device or start emulator  
5.⁠ ⁠Run the app  

## Usage
•⁠  ⁠Type greetings, study, business, or goal-related messages  
•⁠  ⁠AI responds instantly offline  
•⁠  ⁠Chat persists even after rotation  

